Nationâ€™s upliftment.\"}', '{\"1\":\"PO 2: Foster Analytical and critical thinking abilities for data-based decision making.\",\"2\":\"PO 3: Ability to develop Value based Leadership ability.\",\"3\":\"PO 4: Ability to understand, analyze and communicate global, economic, legal, and ethical aspects of business.\",\"4\":\"PO 5: Ability to lead themselves and others in the achievement of organizational goals, contributing effectively to a team environment.\",\"5\":\"PO 6: Attitude to develop the employability skills and design the career meritoriously.\",\"6\":\"PO 7: Develop effective techno-managerial skills and competencies for nurturing future entrepreneurs\",\"7\":\"PO 8: Develop research aptitude that fosters a culture of innovation among students in business by leading edged research and practice in the field.\"}', '{\"4\":\"PSO 1: Apply various concepts and strategies to comprehend the importance of functional and inter-functional disciplines in business management.\",\"1\":\"PSO 2: Recognize opportunities available and face the challenges as competent individuals in the global business environment and adapt accordingly.\",\"2\":\"PSO 3: Formulate & initiate a passion among management graduates for a multidisciplinary knowledge approach for problem-solving, critical analysis and decision making by giving due importance for rational thinking.\",\"3\":\"PSO 4: Channelize the transformation process of every management graduate by providing in-depth knowledge of business management embedded with ethics and a sense of social commitment and imparts value creation and development to the society.\"}', '{\"name\":\"Dr. P. Kannan, MBA., M.Phil., MA(AD&PR)., Ph.D., NET., MISTE., Professor & Head, Department of Management Studies,  P.S.R. Engineering College, Sevalpatti, Sivakasi â€“ 626 140,  Virudhunagar District, Tamil Nadu, India.\",\"email\":\"hod_mba@psr.edu.in\",\"phone\":\"04562-239600 Extention No. 232\"}', '2024-12-31 10:10:54', '2024-12-31 10:10:54');

