(3, 6, NULL, 'Faculty Members', 'RAJ_0885___Copy_1735967614.jpg', '<p>The Electrical and Electronics Engineering (EEE) Department is led by a team of&nbsp; highly qualified and dedicated faculty members. With a unique combination of industrial, academic, and research expertise, the faculty excel in delivering quality education and fostering a culture of innovation.</p>\r\n<p>A significant number of faculty members hold advanced degrees in specialized areas of Electrical and Electronics Engineering, ensuring students receive a well-rounded education that integrates theoretical foundations with practical applications. Their diverse research interests and practical insights enable students to undertake thought-provoking projects that nurture critical thinking, problem-solving, and innovation.</p>\r\n<p>Faculty members employ a mix of traditional and modern teaching methodologies, including blackboards, multimedia tools, and advanced projection systems, to create a dynamic and engaging learning environment. Beyond teaching, they serve as mentors, inspiring students toward academic excellence and equipping them with the skills needed to thrive in the ever-evolving electrical and electronics industry.</p>\r\n<p>Their unwavering dedication to professionalism, lifelong learning, and impactful research ensures that graduates are well-prepared to contribute meaningfully to the global engineering landscape.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '[{\"faculty\":\"Dr.  Muniraj R\",\"qualification\":\"Ph.D\",\"email\":\"muniraj@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-455253373\",\"profileId\":\"261244\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr.  Punitha K\",\"qualification\":\"Ph.D\",\"email\":\"punitha@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-3570767524\",\"profileId\":\"303972\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. Edwin Jose  S\",\"qualification\":\"Ph.D\",\"email\":\"edwinjose@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-4637307601\",\"profileId\":\"332704\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr.  Aruna R\",\"qualification\":\"Ph.D\",\"email\":\"aruna@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-93