(7, 3, NULL, 'Faculty Members', NULL, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2.2; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: justify; color: #333333; font-family: Muli, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">The department\'s faculty represents a diverse array of professionals with robust backgrounds in Biotechnology. Spanning various specialties within the field, including Genetic Engineering, Bioinformatics, Bioprocessing, Molecular Biology, and Biopharmaceuticals, our faculty comprises highly qualified and devoted experts. The majority of our faculty members hold Ph.D. degrees, underscoring their dedication to pioneering research and academic distinction. For those without Ph.D. qualifications, they possess postgraduate degrees, bringing substantial research and academic acumen to our department.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2.2; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: justify; color: #333333; font-family: Muli, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">Remarkably, 90% of our faculty members boast over a decade of experience in both teaching and research within Biotechnology. This breadth of expertise enhances the learning milieu, ensuring students receive an exceptional education grounded in both theoretical principles and practical applications gleaned from real-world scenarios. Ultimately, our faculty members are steadfastly committed to nurturing the next generation of Biotechnologists, equipping students with the requisite skills, knowledge, and expertise to excel in their careers and make impactful contributions to the field of Biotechnology.</p>', '[{\"faculty\":\"Dr. S. Sabarunisha Begum\",\"qualification\":\"M.Tech.,Ph.D.,\",\"email\":\"sabarunisha@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-7332121944\",\"profileId\":\"303916\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. R. Rajeswari\",\"qualification\":\"M.Sc, M.Phil, Ph.D\",\"email\":\"rajeswari@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-429714509\",\"profileId\":\"303913\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. S. Suresh Kumar\",\"qualification\":\"M.Tech.,Ph.D.,\",\"email\":\"sureshkumar@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-7365859461\",\"profileId\":\"303910\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. D. Jansirani\",\"qualification\":\"M.Sc, M.Phil, Ph.D\",\"email\":\"Jansirani@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-43383682306\",\"profileId\":\"344960\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. K. Venkadeswaran\",\"qualification\":\"M.Sc.,Ph.D.,PDF.\",\"email\":\"venkadeswaran@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-7365859469\",\"profileId\":\"303926\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. S. Venkatesh\",\"qualification\":\"M.Sc., Ph.D.\",\"email\":\"venkatesh.s@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-7366317816\",\"profileId\":\"303915\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. P. Muthumari\",\"qualification\":\"M.Tech.,Ph.D.,\",\"email\":\"muthumari@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-43384009811\",\"profileId\":\"327138\"},{\"faculty\":\"Mrs. V. Varalakshmi\",\"qualification\":\"M.Tech.\",\"email\":\"varalakshmi@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-3629114073\",\"profileId\":\"303919\"},{\"faculty\":\"Ms.K. Shalini\",\"qualification\":\"M.Tech.\",\"email\":\"shalini@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-9474963042\",\"profileId\":\"303975\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Mr.K.Perumal\",\"qualification\":\"B.Sc\",\"designation\":\"Lab Technician\"},{\"name\":\"Mrs.P.M.Pushpam\",\"qualification\":\"DME\",\"designation\":\"Lab Technician\"}]', '2024-12-28 09:36:14', '2025-01-02 16:29:53'),
(8, 11, NULL, 'Faculty Members', 'faculty_1735534740.webp', '<p align=\"justify\">The faculty within the department comprises a diverse mix of individuals with extensive industrial and professional backgrounds. Across various domains of mechanical engineering, including Engineering Design, CAD/CAM, Manufacturing/Production Engineering, Industrial Engineering, and Thermal and Energy Engineering, the department boasts qualified and dedicated faculty members. The majority of the faculty hold Ph.D. qualifications, demonstrating their commitment to advanced research and academic excellence. For those faculty members who are not Ph.D. holders, they possess postgraduate degrees and bring considerable research and academic experience to the department.</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Impressively, approximately 75% of the faculty members have accumulated more than 10 years of experience in both teaching and research. This wealth of experience enriches the learning environment and ensures that students receive high-quality education, grounded in both theoretical knowledge and practical insights gained from real-world applications. Overall, the department\'s faculty members are committed to nurturing the next generation of mechanical engineers, equipping students with the skills, knowledge, and expertise needed to excel in their careers and make meaningful contributions to the field of mechanical engineering.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '[{\"faculty\":\"Dr. J. S. Senthilkumaar\",\"qualification\":\"M.E, Ph.D\",\"email\":\"drjssenthil@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-7326565560\",\"profileId\":\"317471\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. P. Pitchipoo\",\"qualification\":\"M.E, Ph.D\",\"email\":\"pitchipoo@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-2184753750\",\"profileId\":\"242049\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr. A. Muthiah\",\"qualification\":\"M.E, Ph.D\",\"email\":\"muthiah@psr.edu.in\",\"uniqueId\":\"1-440109501\",\"profileId\":\"261105\"},{\"faculty\":\"Dr.P.Amuthakkannan\",\"qualification\":\"M.E, Ph.D\",\"email\":\"a