(1, 1, 1, 'Infrastructure', 'jpeg_optimizer_RAJ_0951_11zon_1736743179.jpg', '<p>The Department features well-equipped, air-conditioned laboratories with a wide range of software and equipment that meet industry standards. The following laboratories are available in the Artificial Intelligence and Data Science(AI&amp;DS) department.</p>', '[{\"title\":\"AI&DS Block\",\"description\":\"This is the main building, home to the engineering classrooms and laboratories.\"}]', '2024-10-10 13:48:01', '2025-01-13 04:39:39'),
(2, 9, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '[{\"title\":\"ECE BLOCK - I\",\"description\":\"HOD and Staff Cabins, Class Rooms, Laboratories, Seminar Hall Department Library, Leisure Halls, Rest Rooms, solar plant.\"},{\"title\":\"ECE BLOCK - II\",\"description\":\"Laboratories and Faculty Cabins.\"}]', '2024-12-26 10:31:02', '2025-01-20 05:07:18'),
(3, 5, NULL, 'Infrastructure', 'infrastructure_1735795175.png', '<p>The Department has well equipped Air conditioned laboratories with various softwares and equipments relevant to the industry standards.The following laboratories are associated with CSE department.</p>', '[{\"title\":\"Tera Lab-I\",\"description\":\"Main objective of this laboratory is to provide wide knowledge to the students on various tools of Web Technology, Mobile Application Development, Java and Cloud Computing Environment. Tera Lab â€“ I has 68 Systems which have windows 10 Operating Systems with intel i7 processor and 16GB RAM.\"},{\"title\":\"Tera Lab-II\",\"description\":\"In Tera Lab II, practical courses like Operating Systems Lab, Python, and Machine Learning Practices and Mini Projects are conducted. Tera Lab â€“ II consists of 68 Systems. All the Systems have intel i5 processor and 16GB RAM with windows 10 Operating Systems.\"},{\"title\":\"Tera Lab-III\",\"description\":\"Tera Lab  III is well furnished with modern equipped terminals and loaded with high-end softwares pertaining to the curriculum. This lab is designed for the experiment related to the Computer Networks, Block chain Technology, Software Engineering and Data Structures Laboratory courses. Totally 68 systems are available in this laboratory for students use. All the Systems have intel i3 processor and 8GB RAM with Microsoft Windows 10 and Ubuntu Operating System.\"}]', '2024-12-27 06:41:20', '2025-01-06 05:25:19'),
(4, 10, NULL, 'Infrastructure', 'building_1735376518.jpg', '<p>The Department has well equipped Air conditioned laboratories with many softwares and equipments relevant to the industry standards.The following laboratories are associated with IT department.</p>', '[{\"title\":\"IT Block\",\"description\":\"HOD Room,classes,Lab\",\"imageFile\":\"IT_block_1735376208.png\"}]', '2024-12-28 08:56:49', '2024-12-28 09:01:59'),
(5, 11, NULL, 'Infrastructure', 'infraa_1735538355.jpg', '<p>The department conducts various programs to innovate the technical skills of the students.</p>', '[{\"title\":\"CAD I & II Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The CAD Lab is equipped with advanced software and hardware to facilitate innovative design and engineering solutions for mechanical systems.\"},{\"title\":\"Research Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Research Lab is a cutting-edge facility for advanced prototyping, machining, and fabrication, driving innovation in design and manufacturing solutions.\"},{\"title\":\"Dynamics Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Dynamics Laboratory provides hands-on experience in analyzing motion, forces, and vibrations, essential for understanding mechanical systems\' behavior.\"},{\"title\":\"Metrology and Measurement Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Metrology and Measurement Laboratory equips students and researchers with precision tools and techniques for accurate dimensional and quality analysis.\"},{\"title\":\"Mechatronics Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Mechatronics Laboratory integrates mechanical, electrical, and control systems, fostering innovation in automation and intelligent system design.\"},{\"title\":\"Central Fabrication Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Central Fabrication Lab is a state-of-the-art facility enabling prototype development, advanced machining, and innovative product fabrication.\"},{\"title\":\"Engineering Practices Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Engineering Practices Laboratory provides hands-on training in foundational engineering skills, fostering practical knowledge and technical proficiency.\"},{\"title\":\"Manufacturing Technology Laboratary\",\"description\":\"The Manufacturing Technology Laboratory provides practical training and research opportunities in modern and traditional manufacturing processes for engineering excellence.\"},{\"title\":\"Strength of Materials Laboratory\",\"description\":\"The Strength of Materials Laboratory enables the analysis of material behavior under various loading conditions, fostering a deep understanding of structural integrity and performance.\",\"imageFile\":null},{\"title\":\"Thermal Engineering-I & II Laboratory\",\"description\":\"he Thermal Engineering Laboratory focuses on the study and analysis of heat transfer, thermodynamics, and fluid mechanics to enhance energy systems and thermal management.\",\"imageFile\":\"Thermal_1735629537.jpg\"}]', '2024-12-30 05:59:15', '2024-12-31 07:18:59'),
(6, 3, NULL, 'BIOTECHNOLOGY BLOCK', 'dept_block_1735622359.png', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.28px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">The Biotechnology Department Laboratory boasts state-of-the-art equipment, including HPLC, Gas Chromatography, Bioengineering Fermenter, Thermocycler, CO2 Incubator, ELISA Reader, 2D Gel Electrophoresis, Fluorescent Microscope, Laminar Air Flow Chamber, UV-Vis Spectrophotometer, Gel Documentation System, Deep Freezer, Refrigerated Centrifuge, Cryostat, Lyophilizer, Microfiltration, Ultrafiltration, Double Pipe Heat Exchanger, Fluidization and Packed Column, Plate and Frame Filter Press, and a suite of Bioinformatics software tools.</span></p>', '[{\"title\":\"Bioprocess Engineering Laboratory\",\"description\":\"Bioprocess Engineering Lab equipped with state-of-the-art Bioreactors and a range of supporting Equipmentâ€™s including Refrigerated water bath, Air Compressor, Peristaltic pump, CO2 incubator, HPLC, Orbital shaker, etc., are available in the laboratory. serves as a hub for exploring the frontiers of biotechnology. From cultivating microorganisms to optimizing fermentation processes, bioprocessing techniques drive breakthroughs in the bioprocess laboratory\"},{\"title\":\"Downstream Processing Laboratory\",\"description\":\"Downstream Processing involves separation techniques like chromatography, filtration, and centrifugation to extract and refine biomolecules like proteins, enzymes, and pharmaceuticals, etc., DSP lab is equipped with Gas Chromatography, Ultra filtration unit, Lyophilizer, Sonicator Homogenizer, Dyno mill, Centrifuge, Micro filtration module, etc.,\"},{\"title\":\"Biochemistry Laboratory\",\"description\":\"Biochemistry Laboratory is a facility where biochemical techniques are utilized to analyse biological molecules and their functions. It typically houses equipment for protein purification, DNA sequencing, enzyme assays, and spectrophotometric analysis. Biochemistry lab is equipped with Colorimeter, Spectrophotometer, Heating Mantles, Water baths, Analytical Micro centrifuge, etc.,\"},{\"title\":\"Chemical Engineering Laboratory\",\"description\":\"Chemical Engineering Laboratory is a facility where Chemical Engineering principles are applied to conduct experiments, analyse processes, and develop new technologies. Equipped with instruments such as Simple & Steam Distillation, Orifice &Venturi meter, Double pipe Heat exchanger, Liquid Solid Fluidization, Flow through packed column, Flow through Annular & straight pipe, Plate and frame filter press, Leaf Filter, Muffle furnace, Sieve shaker, etc.\"},{\"title\":\"Genetic Engineering Laboratory\",\"description\":\"Molecular and Genetic Engineering Laboratory is a specialized facility where students to learn genetic material and molecular structures of cells or organisms. Lab is equipped with instruments such as PCR machines, Electrophoresis tank, Gel Documentation System, UV Spectrophotometer, Incubator, Refrigerator, SDS-PAGE electrophoresis, High speed centrifuge, Western blot apparatus, Ice-flake machine, Deep Freezer, UV-trans illuminator, etc.,\"},{\"title\":\"Microbiology Laboratory\",\"description\":\"Microbiology Laboratory is essential tools for magnifying microorganisms and studying their morphology, structure, and behavior. With various types including light and fluorescence microscopes, they enable detailed observation of bacteria, viruses, and fungi. Microbiology Lab is equipped with advanced Microscope, Microbiological Hood for sterilization with UV lighting, Fluorescent Microscope, Orbital Shaker, Autoclave, Refrigerator, ELISA Reader, Incubator, etc.,\"},{\"title\":\"Project laboratory\",\"description\":\"Project laboratory is dedicated solely to the execution of students projects. The other program specific laboratories are also used effectively to run studentâ€™s projects. Project Lab is equipped with HPLC, Orbital shaker and Laminar Flow Hood with UV lighting, etc. Other sophisticated instruments such as Biofermenter, GC, PCR, Transilluminator, Gel documentation system, etc are also used by the students for executing the project works.\"},{\"title\":\"Department Library\",\"description\":\"The Department has Library facilities witharound 180 books. Also it has provision for keeping the reports of project work done by our students. The departmental library also has reading hall that can accommodate about 10 people.\"}]', '2024-12-31 05:19:20', '2024-12-31 05:32:04');

