(3, 4, 1, '', '', '', NULL, '[{\"year\":\"2024\",\"bookChapters\":[{\"bookName\":\"Investigation on Compressive Strength of Fibre-Reinforced Concrete Using Artificial Neural Network, \\\"A. Dhanalakshmi, M. Shahul Hameed, K. Valarmathi & C. Rajendra Prasath \\\" https:\\/\\/link.springer.com\\/chapter\\/10.1007\\/978-981-97-0072-1_2\"}]}]', NULL, '[{\"list\":\"1.\\t\\\"International Conference on Recent Innovation in Science, Engineering, Technology and Management ICETSETM-2016 on 7th & 8th April, 2016.\\\" The International Conference on Recent Innovation in Science, Engineering, Technology, and Management (ICETSETM-2016) was held on the 7th and 8th of April, 2016. This conference provided a multidisciplinary platform for researchers, scholars, and professionals to present and discuss the latest innovations, challenges, and trends across the fields of science, engineering, technology, and management. It aimed to foster collaboration among academia, industry, and government organizations, facilitating the exchange of ideas and knowledge to drive advancements and address contemporary global challenges.\"},{\"list\":\"2.\\t\\\"National Institute of Technical Teachers Training and Research (NITTR) and Department of Civil Engineering and Department of Computer Science Engineering Jointly Organized International Conference on Innovation in Science, Technology and Management Towards Sustainability on 10th November 2017\\\" The National Institute of Technical Teachers Training and Research (NITTTR), in collaboration with the Department of Civil Engineering and the Department of Computer Science Engineering, jointly organized the International Conference on Innovation in Science, Technology, and Management Towards Sustainability on the 10th of November, 2017. This conference aimed to bring together academicians, researchers, industry experts, and policymakers to address the critical need for sustainable solutions in various fields. The event served as a platform to exchange ideas, research findings, and best practices focusing on innovations in science, technology, and management that contribute to environmental, social, and economic sustainability. Discussions and presentations highlighted the importance of interdisciplinary approaches to solving global challenges, including climate change, resource optimization, sustainable urban development, and advancements in information technology. The collaboration between NITTTR and the two key engineering departments underscored the significance of integrating technical expertise with sustainability goals, fostering a holistic understanding of the role of technology and management in achieving sustainable development. By promoting cutting-edge research and encouraging dialogue between participants, the conference contributed to shaping a future-oriented vision for sustainable innovation.\"},{\"list\":\"3.\\t\\\"International Conference on Recent Trends in Civil Engineering, Technology and Management (ICRTCETM-2018) on 12th & 13th April, 2018.\\\" The International Conference on Recent Trends in Civil Engineering, Technology, and Management (ICRTCETM-2018), held on the 12th and 13th of April, 2018, served as a prominent platform for researchers, academics, and industry professionals. The conference focused on the latest advancements, innovations, and challenges in civil engineering, emerging technologies, and management practices. It encouraged knowledge sharing, collaboration, and the development of sustainable solutions to address modern-day engineering and management issues.\"},{\"list\":\"4.\\t\\\"International Conference on Engineering Research 2022 (ICER 2022) on 22nd April 2022\\\"  The International Conference on Engineering Research 2022 (ICER 2022), held on 22nd April 2022, provided a dynamic platform for engineers, researchers, and academicians to showcase their latest findings and innovations across various engineering disciplines. The conference aimed to foster collaboration, exchange of ideas, and discussion on emerging trends, cutting-edge technologies, and challenges in engineering research, contributing to advancements in the field and addressing real-world problems.\\\"\"}]', '2024-12-28 09:06:33', '2024-12-28 10:16:37'),
